videos.headline: Tate takes it 45 yards on the keeper
videos.description: Arizona quarterback Khalil Tate does it himself taking it 45 yards for the score.

videos.headline: Starks dives over the top for the TD
videos.description: Jalen Starks dives over the top of the pile for the 1-yard score in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Tate throws 53-yard strike
videos.description: Khalil Tate hits Shun Brown for a huge gain, setting the Wildcats up in the red zone.

videos.headline: Wilson pounds his way into the end zone
videos.description: Nick Wilson bullies his way in for the touchdown as the Wildcats extend their lead.

videos.headline: Rosen intercepted by Wildcat defense
videos.description: Jace Whittaker picks off Josh Rosen in the end zone and returns it 28 yards.

videos.headline: Whittaker takes 2nd INT to the house
videos.description: Jace Whittaker gets his second interception of the quarter and takes this one 46 yards back for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Jamabo breaks through defenders for TD
videos.description: Soso Jamabo lowers his shoulder and blasts through two defenders on his way to the end zone.

videos.headline: Tate jumps over defender on keeper
videos.description: Khalil Tate shows off his athleticism getting airborne while trying to avoid getting tackled.

videos.headline: Tate connects with Wood for TD
videos.description: Khalil Tate finds Trevor Wood to extend the Wildcats lead in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Olorunfunmi plunges into the end zone
videos.description: Bolu Olorunfunmi  runs through the Wildcat defense for the 4-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Arizona defender ejected for targeting
videos.description: Arizona defensive lineman Parker Zellers is ejected for targeting in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Olorunfunmi rushes for 2nd TD
videos.description: Bolu Olorunfunmi scores his second touchdown of the quarter to close the gap against the Wildcats.

videos.headline: Tate throws perfect 44-yard pass
videos.description: Khalil Tate hits Tony Ellison for a 44-yard gain setting up a Wildcat touchdown.

videos.headline: Wilson scores 2nd TD
videos.description: Nick Wilson runs through the Bruins defense for his second touchdown of the night.

videos.headline: Rosen throws 3rd INT
videos.description: Dane Cruikshank intercepts Josh Rosen in the fourth quarter.
